[Details on the FMDV serotype involved will be helpful.
Jeli is situated in the northern part of peninsular Malaysia, at Lat:
5:42:02N (5.7005), Lon: 101:50:13E (101.837), and can be seen in the
map available at:
<http://www.multimap.com/map//map/browse.cgi?lat=5.7005&lon=101.837&scale=2000000&icon=x>.
